             was indicted for <rs id="t18220522-42-off221" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220522-42-off221" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220522-42-off221" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220522-42-cd222" type="crimeDate">7th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220522-42-off221 t18220522-42-cd222"></join>, one truss of clover hay, value 2 s. 6 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18220522-42-victim391" type="victimName">
                  Sarah Ann 
                  Mountain
               <interp inst="t18220522-42-victim391" type="surname" value="Mountain"></interp>
